<LP>
   Zurn Industries Inc. said it was awarded two contracts
totaling $66 million to design and build combined cycle
cogeneration power plants.
   The Erie, Pa., power equipment maker said one is from a
member of Sithe/Energies Group of New York to build a
56-megawatt plant in Sherill, N.Y. The plant is scheduled to
